          <title>
            <string language="en">Electrophilic substitution reaction of aqueous phenol with bromine water</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Reacción electrophilic de la substitución del

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the equation of the electrophilic substitution reaction of phenol with bromine water forming a white precipitate of 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die Gleichung der 
elektrophilen Ersatzreaktion des Phenols mit Bromwasser, das einen 
weißen Niederschlag von 2,4,6-tribromophenol bildet.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre l'équation de la 
réaction électrophile de substitution du phénol avec de l'eau brome
formant un précipité blanc de 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra a equação da reação 
electrophilic da substituição do phenol com água do bromo que dá 
forma a um precipitate branco de 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra l'equazione della 
reazione elettrofila della sostituzione del fenolo con acqua del bromo
che forma un precipitato bianco di 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει την εξίσωση της 
ηλεκτρονιόφιλης αντίδρασης αντικατάστασης της φαινόλης με το ύδωρ
βρωμίου που διαμορφώνει ένα άσπρο ίζημα 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra la ecuación de la 
reacción electrophilic de la substitución del fenol con agua del 
bromo que forma un precipitado blanco de 2,4,6-tribromophenol.</string>
